This software is a fan-made research and strategy tool for the cozy
tavern-management game *Travellers Rest* by Louqou Productions
(https://store.steampowered.com/app/1139980/Travellers_Rest/).

It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Louqou.

The tool reads game data from a local Travellers Rest install owned by
the user. No copyrighted game assets, sprites, localization strings, or
ScriptableObject data are bundled with this repository — they are extracted
from the user's own copy of the game by the scripts in `scripts/`.
